        Clause 20 [<span class="italic">Annual report and forward plans</span>]:
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0585P0-01918'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0585P0_19980129_GCR_111' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        [<span class="italic">Amendment No. 44 not moved.</span>]
      </p>
      <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_134gc' title='Col. 134GC &mdash; HL Deb 29 January 1998 vol 585 c134GC' name='column_134gc' href='#column_134gc' rel='bookmark'>134GC</a>
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0585P0-01919'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0585P0_19980129_GCR_112' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
